# NOTE: unlike every other chart in this repo, we intentionally COMMIT the vendored upstream tarball
# (charts/cluster-0.7.0.tgz) — so there is deliberately NO `charts/*.tgz` ignore rule here.
#
# Why: this chart is a file:// dependency of workloads, and it in turn pins a REMOTE dependency
# (cnpg/cluster). ArgoCD's repo-server runs `helm dependency build` only at the top level, so it won't
# fetch this transitive remote dependency over the network at render time. Vendoring it in git is the
# reliable path (the file:// package carries it along). Refresh it with `helm dependency update` here and
# re-commit both Chart.lock and charts/cluster-0.7.0.tgz when bumping the pin in Chart.yaml.
